title: Pushups
body: Pushups work multiple muscle groups, strengthening the arms, chest, and shoulders.

title: Lunges
body: Lunges work the thighs, buttocks, hips, and abdominal muscles.

title: Planks
body: Planks strengthen the back and abdominal muscles and help build core strength.

title: Dumbbelling
body: Dumbbell rows can strengthen the back and increase muscle growth.

title: Glute bridge
body: Glute bridge is good for muscles in the back body, called the posterior chain.

title: Knee tucks
body: Knee tucks work the abdominals, calves, and shins by using an exercise ball.
